'''Muja muffins''' were a type of [[Muffin/Legends|muffin]] with [[Muja fruit/Legends|muja fruit]] and nuts that were favored by the [[Daan (people)/Legends|Daan]]. The pastry originated from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Gala]].<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|II|341|Muja muffin}}</ref>

